msgid "Duelist Wizards are a rare group of mages, who instead of studying magic deeper and deeper decided to start using it to defeat other mages. The main motivation of this was of course the desire to get higher in ranks among other magi, who usually underestimate them because of their weaker knowledge of magical theories. Their philosophy is not based on the seek of knowledge, but on the desire to be stronger than other magi."
