msgid "Voracious Herb is one of the few plants adopted to the hostile environment in Inferno after Uria's arrival. They are dangerous even to approach, and their main source of food are creatures living around, imps and demons, but if more interesting prey is nearby, they leave them alone. They are extremely dangerous in proximity of symbiotic mushrooms."
